# Deny everything by default, then allow only the Quarkus build output.
# `!target/quarkus-app` is the dir; `!target/quarkus-app/**` is needed to
# recursively re-include subdirs (lib/, app/, quarkus/) — without it `*`
# at the top still matches their contents.
*
!target/quarkus-app
!target/quarkus-app/**
